        <para id="id1165967153339">Thus one can use T<sub>1</sub> or T<sub>2</sub> relaxation experiment to determine the specific surface area. We shall explain the case of the T<sub>2</sub> technique further as <link target-id="id1165969730126"/>. </para>
        <equation id="id1165969730126">
